'''Andromeda X''' (And 10) is a [[dwarf spheroidal galaxy]] about [[1 E22 m|2.9 million]] [[light-year]]s away from the [[Sun]] in the [[constellation]] [[Andromeda (constellation)|Andromeda]].  Discovered in 2005, And X is a [[satellite galaxy]] of the [[Andromeda Galaxy]] (M31).

